{"tid":2262644,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"仲有幾多人記得自焚者呢幾幕?","createTime":"2020-10-29T09:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T18:36:04.000Z","uid":12599,"like":96,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ffbcf430117545864f754589dfc331f9dd373ec8","tid":2262644,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:13:58.000Z","msg":"學生動源19歲入獄, 戲入面係21歲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/49oFQcp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49oFQcp.jpg&h=9c7b79e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CSWW7XO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCSWW7XO.jpg&h=7658ec07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyo6LLK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcyo6LLK.jpg&h=caadd3e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年反送中後立國安法, 劇入面係2020年立既係23條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MrbHi5K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMrbHi5K.jpg&h=ec14841c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國難五金 + 國安人員<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GReNvcq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGReNvcq.jpg&h=d2909b92&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nKOL評中共<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tjv5gSq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjv5gSq.jpg&h=d5e17cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獄中手足既信息, 比戲入面又沉重<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTvAD5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTvAD5M.jpg&h=43959f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一幕無限loop左大半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qzYBSr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qzYBSr.jpg&h=0eac495a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後一幕唔post啦, 現實比戲入面更加離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98202eeee8e8f10c7ce7633dc21604f287cdac3","tid":2262644,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:16:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eff7c6e5fc41223203f3d4d4dc68413d0bdb5205","tid":2262644,"uid":366245,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"376a58a1cb51bd5bc95a610bf3c973187927c63e","tid":2262644,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85b3290f852689e6aa3168ebb7d75afad0fb13f","tid":2262644,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:53:33.000Z","msg":"淨係諗起叔一燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2579d8d82c75eb19feea814e2dcb97e58322150","tid":2262644,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ddc252f727357b5b81ae3ad245077334b14173","tid":2262644,"uid":245849,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:56:29.000Z","msg":"十年。不用"},{"pid":"c38c01f4741b2b09825723a1713c846fe85075d4","tid":2262644,"uid":288252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:59:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa45f3a93826160bf278f19673b212362435e284","tid":2262644,"uid":67816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02f2da12d088ed